{"ID":"20260605145800-ausdvcp","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605145800-ausdvcp","title":"2021年新高考Ⅰ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605145854"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605145815-c9yqi7a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145815-c9yqi7a","updated":"20260605145815"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"寄江州白司马"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"①"}]},{"ID":"20260605145815-jeemtq3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145815-jeemtq3","updated":"20260605145815"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杨巨源"}]},{"ID":"20260605145815-f263hw7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145815-f263hw7","updated":"20260605145815"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"江州司马平安否？惠远东林住得无​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"②"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​？"}]},{"ID":"20260605145815-k6oy0rr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145815-k6oy0rr","updated":"20260605145815"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"湓浦曾闻似衣带，庐峰见说胜香炉。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145815-w6olqhb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145815-w6olqhb","updated":"20260605145815"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题诗岁晏离鸿断，望阙天遥病鹤孤。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145815-vnsdfiv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145815-vnsdfiv","updated":"20260605145815"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莫谩拘牵雨花社​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"③"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，青云依旧是前途。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145815-8jnlvbt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145815-8jnlvbt","updated":"20260605145815"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【注】①江州白司马：即白居易。②惠远：东晋高僧，居庐山东林寺。③莫谩：不要。雨花社：指佛教讲经的集会。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145800-zl8nq2d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605145800-zl8nq2d","updated":"20260605145827"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605145827-h3xyzxa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145827-h3xyzxa","updated":"20260605145827"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．下列对这首诗的理解和赏析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605145827-hru3bxu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145827-hru3bxu","updated":"20260605145827"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．根据内容分析，这首诗的写作时间应该与白居易的《琵琶行》比较接近。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145827-zsl54jp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145827-zsl54jp","updated":"20260605145827"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．第三句使用“一衣带水”的典故，表现出朋友之间“天涯若比邻”之意。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145827-5sym704","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145827-5sym704","updated":"20260605145827"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．第六句中的“病鹤”指的是白居易，他怀恋长安，时常遥望京城的宫阙。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145827-nzn4g8u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145827-nzn4g8u","updated":"20260605145827"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．诗人最后开解朋友，目前虽然身处贬谪之中，但未来的前途依然很远大。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145827-827wyxl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145827-827wyxl","updated":"20260605145827"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．前人论此诗，认为第二句已包含委婉劝告的意思，对这一观点应怎样理解？请简要分析。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145800-bc899z2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605145800-bc899z2","updated":"20260605145841"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605145840-qcz8pxf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145840-qcz8pxf","updated":"20260605145841"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．B    16．“劝诫”是这首诗的主旨，诗人在尾联点明该主旨，劝说白居易不要沉迷于宗教，消磨了志气，要对人生充满信心；②诗歌的第二句在问候中提到僧人和寺庙，为结尾正式的劝诫做了铺垫。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145800-3xbq4cq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605145800-3xbq4cq","updated":"20260605145854"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605145854-wjhvzul","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145854-wjhvzul","updated":"20260605145854"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．本题考查学生理解思想内容、赏析艺术特色的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145854-krjhf88","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145854-krjhf88","updated":"20260605145854"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.第三句是说诗人曾经听说湓水萦绕像衣带，是对此地景物的描绘，并未有表现朋友间“天涯若比邻”之意，此项对用典解释有误。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145854-we8fk7d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145854-we8fk7d","updated":"20260605145854"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145854-wv4avkx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145854-wv4avkx","updated":"20260605145854"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．本题考查学生理解分析思想内容的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145854-bm0wo5p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145854-bm0wo5p","updated":"20260605145854"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题干中的“含委婉劝告之意”，已提示考生解答此题的关键，诗人采用哪些手法劝告了什么，既要对诗句的表现手法作出判断，又要体会出诗句中隐含的意思。诗中体现劝告之意的是 “惠远东林住得无？”和“莫谩拘牵雨花社，青云依旧是前途”两句。前者借典故用问句，后者直接表达劝慰之意。只要结合这两句诗，把诗人蕴含其中的意思和情感答出即可。"}]},{"ID":"20260605145800-njp2hua","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605145800-njp2hua","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}